      <item>
        <title>Travis CLI in Docker container</title>
        <description>&lt;h1&gt;Dockerfile&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dockerfile used to build an image with &lt;code class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;Travis CLI&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-dockerfile highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt; ruby:alpine&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;RUN &lt;/span&gt;apk add &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;--no-cache&lt;/span&gt; build-base git &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;se&quot;&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;    gem install travis &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;se&quot;&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;    gem install travis-lint &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;se&quot;&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;    apk del build-base &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;se&quot;&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;    mkdir workspace

&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;VOLUME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt; [&quot;/workspace&quot;]&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;ENTRYPOINT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;s&quot;&gt; [&quot;travis&quot;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;docker build --tag jootl\travis-cli .
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;Usage&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To use, for example, the encryption tool :&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;language-bash highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;docker &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;-it&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nt&quot;&gt;--rm&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
        <pubDate>Tue, 04 Dec 2018 11:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
